### Performance Testing - Multiple Requests
### =============================================================================

### 11. Batch Summarization Test (Run this 3-5 times to test performance)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/documents/summarize
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "Brief test note: Patient stable, vitals normal, continue current treatment."
}

